sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as UI (React)
    participant API as graph_search_api :8005
    participant Engine as graph_search_engine
    participant Neptune as Neptune Analytics

    User->>UI: Navigate to /graph-search
    UI->>UI: Load vis.js script
    UI->>API: GET /api/config
    API->>Engine: Read graph_config.yaml
    Engine-->>API: colors, icons, sizes, examples
    API-->>UI: ServerConfig JSON

    Note over UI: Spinner: Loading graph data...

    UI->>API: GET /api/graph?limit=500
    API->>Engine: get_graph_data(limit)
    Engine->>Neptune: openCypher MATCH query
    Neptune-->>Engine: nodes + edges
    Engine-->>API: GraphData
    API-->>UI: { nodes, edges }

    Note over UI: Spinner: Rendering 150 nodes...

    UI->>UI: vis.js Network created
    UI->>UI: Physics stabilization

    Note over UI: stabilizationIterationsDone → Graph visible
